review.reviewBody: i didn't have enough for gravy so i asked them in the notes and they gave me gravy, best doordash order ever!!
Everything was hot and made with all the adjustments requested
again they forgot something.  every time. obviously they don't pay attention to detail.
The fries in Mozza Burger® Combo are very dry and not appetizing. Chicken Buddy Burger® was cold and not freshly made.
Dry burger. Chicken was soaked in dressing. Both inedible
